API Spec
========

*we need to authenticate the user before doing these

Login (POST)
	index.php/api/auth/login
	index.php/api/auth/create
	index.php/api/auth/logout
	index.php/api/auth/forgot
	index.php/api/auth/reset

	token eg:
	localhost/MobileHub/index.php/auth/reset/sahan.serasinghe@gmail.com/e3afed0047b08059d0fada10f400c1e56

Question (GET/POST)
	index.php/api/question/post
	index.php/api/question/details/{id}
	index.php/api/question/delete/
	index.php/api/question/update/

	index.php/api/question/close

	index.php/api/question/flag

	index.php/api/question/recent/offset
	index.php/api/question/popular/offset
	index.php/api/question/unanswered/offset
	index.php/api/question/all/offset

Answer
	index.php/api/answer/post/
	index.php/api/answer/delete/{id}/
	index.php/api/answer/update/{id}/

	index.php/api/answer/promote/ - POST

Vote
	index.php/api/vote/voteup/question/{id}
	index.php/api/vote/votedown/question/{id}
	index.php/api/vote/voteup/answer/{id}
	index.php/api/vote/votedown/answer/{id}

Tags
	index.php/api/tag/post/question/id
	index.php/api/tag/delete/question/id
	index.php/api/tag/update/question/id
	index.php/api/tag/get/question/id

	index.php/api/tags/all

	index.php/api/tags/recent/offset/tag/{tagname}
	index.php/api/tags/popular/offset/tag/{tagname}
	index.php/api/tags/unanswered/offset/tag/{tagname}
	index.php/api/tags/all/offset/tag/{tagname}

Search
	index.php/api/search/questions/Q+
	index.php/api/search/questions/advanced/Q+

	index.php/api/search/users/Q+

	index.php/api/search/tags/Q+

User
	index.php/api/user/details/{username}/
	index.php/api/user/fulldetails/{username}/

	post
	index.php/api/user/post/{username}

	index.php/api/user/delete/
	index.php/api/user/changepassword/{username}

Admin - All POST
	index.php/api/admin/details/basic
	index.php/api/admin/details/logins

	index.php/api/admin/question/details

	index.php/api/admin/answer/details

	index.php/api/admin/user/details
	index.php/api/admin/user/delete

	index.php/api/admin/user/students
	index.php/api/admin/user/promote

	index.php/api/admin/requests/tutor
	index.php/api/admin/requests/delete

	index.php/api/admin/tutor/accept
	index.php/api/admin/tutor/decline

	index.php/api/admin/deletion/accept